00:02:00.860 --> 00:02:04.920
This dish is so beautiful you can actually take the pan right to the table

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:08.140
and because we've steamed the raw shrimp

00:02:08.140 --> 00:02:11.600
they are so delicate and flavorful.

